#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Screen"
msgstr "Mänguväli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Game screen is in the center of the screen and is the largest section of "
"the window."
msgstr "Mänguväli asub akna keskel ja on selle suurim osa."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Statusbar"
msgstr "Olekuriba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Status bar is located at the bottom of the screen. It displays how many "
"pieces are left currently and the game timer, which keeps track of the "
"elapsed time from the start of the game until the game is finished."
msgstr ""
"Olekuriba asub mänguvälja all. See näitab, kui palju kive on parajasti "
"alles, samuti taimerit, mis hoiab silma peal mängu algusest selle lõpuni "
"kuluval ajal."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "The KSame Mode"
msgstr "KSame'i režiim"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "&klickety; provides a &ksame; scoring mode."
msgstr "&klickety; pakub &ksame;'i tulemuste arvestamise režiimi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "The score is calculated as follows:"
msgstr "Tulemust arvutatakse nii:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Subtract 2 from the number of marbles erased, and square the result."
msgstr "Eemaldatud nuppude arvust lahutatakse 2 ja tulemus võetakse ruutu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "As an example, if you erase 7 balls, then you get 25 points (7 minus 2 = "
#| "5. 5 squared is 25 points).If you erase 8 balls, then you get 36 points "
#| "(8 minus 2 = 6. 6 squared is 36 points."
msgid ""
"As an example, if you erase 7 balls, then you get 25 points (7 minus 2 = 5, "
"5 squared is 25 points). If you erase 8 balls, then you get 36 points (8 "
"minus 2 = 6, 6 squared is 36 points)."
msgstr ""
"Kui näiteks eemaldad seitse nuppu, saad 25 punkti (7 miinus 2 võrdub 5 ja 5 "
"ruudus on 25). Kui eemaldad 8 nuppu, saad 36 punkti (8 miinus 2 võrdub 6 ja "
"6 ruudus on 36)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Get as many of the same pieces as you can, and then erase them in one click. "
"That way you will get a higher score. The game is over when there are no "
"pieces that can be erased."
msgstr ""
"Vaata, kuidas sul õnnestuks kokku saada võimalikult suur ühesuguste nuppude "
"kogum - selle eemaldamisega teenid rohkem punkte. Mäng on läbi, kui enam ei "
"ole võimalik ühtegi nupuühendit eemaldada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The score will then be decreased according to the number of remaining "
"pieces. If you erase all pieces 1,000 bonus points will be added to the "
"final score."
msgstr ""
"Seejärel väheneb tulemus lauale jäänud nuppude võrra. Kui oled eemaldanud "
"kõik nupud, saad boonuseks 1000 punkti juurde."

